<br>
ToN did make a mistake, we all agree on that. We've never really had  an incident where we've gone in under FiF (which we had, moving in when TWC had wiped), and had the other guild not respect that claim. We didnt imagine that TWC would actually just bumrush the mob when we were moving into position, and I think we probably expected a GM decision Before Seru was engaged.<br>
<br>
